sellerCard.oneLiner: Always deliver more good than expected
sellerCard.description:
Hi there! My name is Muhammad Naveed and I am an experienced web developer with expertise in front-end, back-end, and test-driven development. I hold a BS in Computer Science and have over 5 years of experience in building scalable web applications.

I have worked with large startups, groups, and organizations, both individually and as part of a team. My areas of expertise include building and deploying large-scale applications, Ruby on Rails, MERN Stack, test-driven development, continuous integration, Javascript/jQuery, React, and databases like Postgresql, MySql, and MongoDB.

description.content:
Welcome to my Ruby on Rails Gig!

I am an experienced Ruby on Rails developer, committed to delivering high-quality code and exceptional service to my clients. With three years of experience in web development, I am confident in my ability to provide you with the solutions you need to make your project a success.


My services include:

  • Custom website development
  • Devise authentication
  • Gems installation
  • Test-driven development, CI/CD
  • RSpec testing and feature testing
  • Zapier (Email integration)
  • Payment integration (Stripe)
  • RESTful APIs
  • Social APIs: Google, Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter, Outlook, WhatsApp
  • Front-end development with React, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
  • Deployment on Heroku and AWS(Elastic beanstalk)


I am dedicated to meeting deadlines and providing my clients with the best possible results. With my unlimited revisions policy, you can be sure that you will get exactly what you are looking for.


Please feel free to contact me with any questions or to discuss your project in more detail. Let's work together to make your project a success!
